# Node.js Learning Projects 🚀


A collection of mini-projects and practice tasks as I learn Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB.

## 📁 Projects Included

- `01-hello-world` – Basic Hello World script
- `02-http-server` – Simple HTTP server using core modules
- `03-express-basics` – middleware and basic express modules
- `04-Login-form ` – Login form using node and express

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express

